        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Thu Jul 23 2020 23:23:12 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><ul><li><a href="#markdown介绍">Markdown介绍</a></li><li><a href="#typora简介">Typora简介</a></li><li><a href="#typora常用快捷键"><strong>Typora常用快捷键</strong></a></li><li><a href="#markdown语法">Markdown语法</a><ul><li><a href="#1-目录">1 目录</a></li><li><a href="#2-标题">2 标题</a></li><li><a href="#3-字体">3 字体</a></li><li><a href="#4-引用">4 引用</a></li><li><a href="#5-分割线">5 分割线</a></li><li><a href="#6-图片">6 图片</a><ul><li><a href="#61-本地图片">6.1 本地图片</a></li><li><a href="#62-网络图片">6.2 网络图片</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#7-列表">7 列表</a><ul><li><a href="#71-无序列表">7.1 无序列表</a></li><li><a href="#72-有序列表">7.2 有序列表</a></li><li><a href="#73-任务列表">7.3 任务列表</a></li><li><a href="#74-列表嵌套">7.4 列表嵌套</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#8-表格">8 表格</a></li><li><a href="#9-代码">9 代码</a></li><li><a href="#10-链接">10 链接</a></li><li><a href="#11-脚注">11 脚注</a></li></ul></li></ul><h1><span id="markdown介绍">Markdown介绍</span></h1><p>Markdown 是一种<strong>纯文本格式的标记语言</strong>。</p><h1><span id="typora简介">Typora简介</span></h1><p>Typora是一款<strong>支持即时渲染（实时预览）的Markdown文本编辑器</strong>。</p><h1><span id="typora常用快捷键"><strong>Typora常用快捷键</strong></span></h1><table><thead><tr><th align="center">快捷键</th><th align="center">功能</th><th align="center">快捷键</th><th align="center">功能</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 1</td><td align="center">一级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + B</td><td align="center">字体加粗</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 2</td><td align="center">二级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + I</td><td align="center">字体倾斜</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 3</td><td align="center">三级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + U</td><td align="center">下划线</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 4</td><td align="center">四级标题</td><td align="center">Alt + Shift + 5</td><td align="center">删除线</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 5</td><td align="center">五级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + T</td><td align="center">插入表格</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 6</td><td align="center">六级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + K</td><td align="center">插入链接</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + L</td><td align="center">选中一行</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + I</td><td align="center">插入图片</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + D</td><td align="center">选中一个单词</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + M</td><td align="center">插入公式</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + E</td><td align="center">选中相同格式的文字</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + Q</td><td align="center">插入引用</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + Home</td><td align="center">返回顶部</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + K</td><td align="center">插入代码块</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + End</td><td align="center">返回底部</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Enter</td><td align="center">跳出代码块另起一行</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + F</td><td align="center">查找</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + `</td><td align="center">插入代码片段</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + H</td><td align="center">替换</td><td align="center">Shift + Tab</td><td align="center">向前缩进</td></tr></tbody></table><h1><span id="markdown语法">Markdown语法</span></h1><h2><span id="1-目录">1 目录</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[toc]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li><p>安装：安装一个<code>hexo-toc</code>的插件，代码如下：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="BASH"><figure class="iseeu highlight /bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-toc --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li></ul><ul><li><p>配置：配置站点配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="YAML"><figure class="iseeu highlight /yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">maxdepth:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>使用：在Markdown文章中加入toc的占位符：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- toc --&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li></ul><h2><span id="2-标题">2 标题</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li><p><code>#</code>与<code>标题内容</code>之间一定要有空格</p></li><li><p>快捷键：一到六阶标题：<code>Ctrl + 1/2/3/4/5/6</code></p><p>​ 普通文本： <code>Ctrl + 0</code></p></li></ul><h2><span id="3-字体">3 字体</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*倾斜字体*</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**加粗字体**</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***加粗倾斜字**</span>*</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span>这是加下划线的文字<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">~~这是加删除线的文字~~  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span>居中文本<span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">==高亮文本==</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li><p>快捷键：<em>倾斜</em>：<code>Ctrl + I</code></p><p>​ <strong>加粗</strong>：<code>Ctrl + B</code></p><p>​ <u>下划线</u>：<code>Ctrl + U</code></p><p>​ <del>删除线</del>：<code>Alt + Shift + 5</code></p><center>居中文本</center><p>​ ==高亮文本==</p></li></ul><h2><span id="4-引用">4 引用</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;引用</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;引用</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt;引用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>效果如下：</p><blockquote><p>引用</p><blockquote><p>引用</p><blockquote><p>引用</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><ul><li>输入<code>&gt;</code>后面加空格可以连续嵌套</li><li>快捷键：<code>Ctrl + Shift + Q</code></li></ul><h2><span id="5-分割线">5 分割线</span></h2><p>三个以上<code>-</code>或<code>*</code></p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>注意：创建.md文件后首行（必须是第一行）输入<code>---</code>，然后回车即可插入<code>Front-matter</code>。</p><h2><span id="6-图片">6 图片</span></h2><p>图片语法格式如下：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt 属性文本</span>](<span class="link">图片地址</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt 属性文本</span>](<span class="link">图片地址 "可选标题"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>高级插入图片（类似高级链接）：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这个链接用 pig 作为网址变量 [<span class="string">百度猪图片</span>][<span class="symbol">pig</span>]</span><br><span class="line">然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">pig</span>]: <span class="link">https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&amp;quality=80&amp;size=b9999_10000&amp;sec=1595155655173&amp;di=7ef9b7285e79ee09de09d3196ef40f8f&amp;imgtype=0&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fres.fsonline.com.cn%2Fa%2F10001%2F201811%2F982345d2a660e22ed247148e81518c0b.gif</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>效果如下：</p><p>这个链接用 pig 作为网址变量 <a href="https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1595155655173&di=7ef9b7285e79ee09de09d3196ef40f8f&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2Fres.fsonline.com.cn%2Fa%2F10001%2F201811%2F982345d2a660e22ed247148e81518c0b.gif" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度猪图片</a><br>然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）</p><h3><span id="61-本地图片">6.1 本地图片</span></h3><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">直接拖进来</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><img src="/1011929149/pig.gif" alt></p><ul><li><p>解决博客部署后不显示图片的方法：</p><ul><li><p>安装插件：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="BASH"><figure class="iseeu highlight /bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-asset-image --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>修改博客配置：修改博客根目录中<code>_config.yml</code>文件的配置项<code>post_asset_folder</code>为<code>true</code>：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="YAML"><figure class="iseeu highlight /yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>本地图片放置：将需要引用的本地图片存放在与文章名相同的文件夹中（有时要手动新建）。</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3><span id="62-网络图片">6.2 网络图片</span></h3><p><img src="https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1595155655173&di=7ef9b7285e79ee09de09d3196ef40f8f&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2Fres.fsonline.com.cn%2Fa%2F10001%2F201811%2F982345d2a660e22ed247148e81518c0b.gif" alt></p><ul><li>网络图片链接：用检查元素<code>F12</code>提取网络地址（如：xxx.jpg）。</li><li>快捷键：插入图片：<code>Ctrl + Shift + I</code></li></ul><h2><span id="7-列表">7 列表</span></h2><h3><span id="71-无序列表">7.1 无序列表</span></h3><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>列表内容  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>列表内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>列表内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>注意：<code>- + *</code> 都可使用，且与内容之间必须要有一个空格 。</p><h3><span id="72-有序列表">7.2 有序列表</span></h3><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>列表内容  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>列表内容  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3. </span>列表内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>注意：<code>数字 + 实心点</code>与<code>列表内容</code>之间必须要有一个空格。</p><h3><span id="73-任务列表">7.3 任务列表</span></h3><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[ ] 橘子</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[x] 苹果</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>[ ] 香蕉</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>效果如下：</p><ul><li><input disabled type="checkbox"> 橘子</li><li><input checked disabled type="checkbox"> 苹果</li><li><input disabled type="checkbox"> 香蕉</li></ul><h3><span id="74-列表嵌套">7.4 列表嵌套</span></h3><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>嵌套</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>嵌套</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>嵌套</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>嵌套</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>嵌套</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3. </span>嵌套</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>效果如下：（可直接使用Tab键）</p><ul><li>嵌套<ul><li>嵌套<ul><li>嵌套<ol><li>嵌套<ol start="2"><li>嵌套<ol start="3"><li>嵌套</li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h2><span id="8-表格">8 表格</span></h2><ul><li><p>输入 <code>| 表头1 | 表头2 |</code>并回车，即可创建一个包含2元素的列表</p><table><thead><tr><th>表头1</th><th>表头2</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></li><li><p>快捷键 ：<code>Ctrl + T</code>（可设置行数和列数）</p></li><li><p>例子：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|表头1|表头2|表头3|</span><br><span class="line">|-|:--:|---:|</span><br><span class="line">|内容1|内容2|内容3|</span><br><span class="line">|内容4|内容5|内容6|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>效果如下：</p><table><thead><tr><th>表头1</th><th align="center">表头2</th><th align="right">表头3</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>内容1</td><td align="center">内容2</td><td align="right">内容3</td></tr><tr><td>内容4</td><td align="center">内容5</td><td align="right">内容6</td></tr></tbody></table><ul><li>第一行为表头，第二行为分割表头和主体部分，第三行开始每一行为一个表格行。</li><li>列与列之间用管道符号<code>|</code> 隔开。</li><li><code>-</code>有一个就行，为了对齐，可以多加几个。</li><li>文字默认居左；<br><code>-</code>两边加<code>:</code>表示文字居中；<br><code>-</code>右边加<code>:</code>表示文字居右。</li></ul></li></ul><h2><span id="9-代码">9 代码</span></h2><ul><li><p>插入代码块：<code>Ctrl + Shift + K</code>或输入```(language)，再回车。</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">​<span class="code">```</span>(~~~) language</span><br><span class="line">​<span class="code">```</span>              -&gt;普通文本</span><br><span class="line">​<span class="code">```</span>c             -&gt;c</span><br><span class="line">​<span class="code">```</span>python        -&gt;python </span><br><span class="line">​<span class="code">```</span>c++           -&gt;c++</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>切换到下一行：<code>Ctrl + Enter</code></p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">printf("Hello World!")</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>光标在这儿（在代码块中跳出代码块另起一行）。</p></li><li><p>插入代码片段：Ctrl + Shift + `或输入``，再在符号之间加内容。</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`printf("Hello World!")`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>效果如下：</p><p><code>printf(&quot;Hello World!&quot;)</code></p></li></ul><h2><span id="10-链接">10 链接</span></h2><p>插入链接：<code>Ctrl + K</code></p><ul><li><p>不显示链接地址</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">百度</span>](<span class="link">https://www.baidu.com</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a></p></li><li><p>显示链接地址</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">https:</span>//<span class="attr">www.baidu.com</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><a href="https://www.baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.baidu.com</a></p></li></ul><p>高级链接：</p><ul><li><p>可以通过变量设置一个链接，变量赋值在文档末尾进行：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这个链接用 coco 作为网址变量 [<span class="string">cocofafa</span>][<span class="symbol">coco</span>]</span><br><span class="line">这个链接用 baidu 作为网址变量 [<span class="string">Baidu</span>][<span class="symbol">baidu</span>]</span><br><span class="line">然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">coco</span>]: <span class="link">https://www.cocofafa.com/</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">baidu</span>]: <span class="link">https://www.baidu.com/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>效果如下：</p><p>这个链接用 coco 作为网址变量 <a href="https://www.cocofafa.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cocofafa</a><br>这个链接用 baidu 作为网址变量 <a href="https://www.baidu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Baidu</a><br>然后在文档的结尾为变量赋值（网址）</p></li></ul><h2><span id="11-脚注">11 脚注</span></h2><ul><li><p>脚注的格式如下：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[^要注明的文本]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>脚注的用法如下：</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="MARKDOWN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">创建脚注格式如[^Cocofafa]。</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^Cocofafa</span>]:<span class="link">博客名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>效果如下（如右上角参考文献的数字角标）：</p><p>创建脚注格式如<a href="博客名">^Cocofafa</a>。</p></li></ul><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
      
      
